{"tid":2089313,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"大家留意下今日警甴同政府出嘅聲明，佢地開始想批鬥傳媒同網媒","createTime":"2020-07-01T15:04:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T15:12:08.000Z","uid":66260,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"783d477f0222c00b164828242310b3c1c925eb9c","tid":2089313,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:04:16.000Z","msg":"警方強烈譴責蘋果日報顛倒是非，背離新聞道德 感到極度憤慨和不齒<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2089276\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2089276</a><br />\n<br />\npopo對網媒顛倒是非 表示震怒<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2088717\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2088717</a><br />\n【有網媒將暴徒襲擊警員的事件形容為「市民合力擊退落單警」 警方表示震怒】<br />\n<br />\n警方：有網媒以特寫鏡頭拍攝時代廣場印有警員資料的紙張<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2089215\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2089215</a><br />\n警方認為有關舉動等同加添對被起底警員的傷害，極不恰當。事實上，以廣角鏡頭拍攝同樣可達致報道的效果。警方對有關舉動表示遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n［國安法］政府聲明：高度讚揚警隊堅守崗位，強烈譴責暴徒及極不負責任媒體！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2089284\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2089284</a><br />\n政府發言人對於這些無法無天的暴行和極不負責任的報導予以強烈譴責。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">估計政府好快會用蟈安法郁網媒</span>"},{"pid":"b713907276a02d6f9cbbc7a046742939bcda2226","tid":2089313,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:05:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6213fa152f43f9bdc8aaa6f3cf5e2f04219ebff9","tid":2089313,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:05:46.000Z","msg":"又加速<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b013297275ff008f0017a1171edbac0405ade7f","tid":2089313,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:05:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.g